author: Scott Fleishman
title: Frenzy play of the week- Week 7
text: Our Play of the Week for Week 7, winning by just over fifty votes, goes to St. Johnsbury Junior quarterback Collin Urie. He scores one of his two first half touchdowns with an impressive effort including a leap over a defender in the endzone. That play beat out a juggling catch by Burlington's Kevin Garrison and an overpowering touchdown run from BFA's Nate Parady .
